'''Lu-ramin''' was an oil mined on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Ebra]]. It was a vital component of several medicines, as well as the beverage [[Ebran Lu-ramin Oilmead]].

The [[Ebranite]]s traditionally sold lu-ramin to the [[Carosite]]s, who presumably prized it for its medical properties. However, while [[Ebra]] was under the repressive rule of [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Governor/Legends|governor]] [[Evitch Jenton]], this trade was cut off in favor of Imperial-allied corporations and [[Species/Legends|species]]. Much of the lu-ramin [[Mining/Legends|mined]] at this time came from mines in the [[Grythsorin]] canyon system, which was worked by political [[Prisoner/Legends|prisoners]] and [[Exile (punishment)/Legends|exiles]].

